<div class="learn-page">
    <h1 class="mb-3">Learn Mermaid &amp; Temporal</h1>
    <p class="lead text-muted mb-4">
        This page points developers and business colleagues to trusted resources for understanding Mermaid (diagrams) and Temporal (workflows). 
        Use the tables below to jump to official docs, tutorials, and videos.
    </p>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="mb-3">Mermaid</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">
            <strong>Mermaid</strong> is a JavaScript-based diagramming tool that turns text definitions into diagrams. You write simple, Markdown-inspired syntax (e.g. <code>flowchart TD</code>, <code>A --> B</code>) and Mermaid renders flowcharts, sequence diagrams, and more. It powers the workflow diagrams on this dashboard and is widely used in docs, wikis, and apps.
        </p>
