    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="mb-3">Temporal</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">
            <strong>Temporal</strong> is a workflow platform that runs durable, reliable application logic. Workflows are long-running processes that survive restarts and failures; activities are units of work (e.g. API calls, DB updates). Temporal handles retries, timeouts, and state so you can focus on business logic. This dashboard discovers and visualizes workflows written with the Temporal .NET SDK.
